{"tid":1548428,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【養兔潮流】兔子不親人的誤會而被棄養 !","createTime":"2019-09-07T04:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:14:01.000Z","uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a354e56edcfe779c2e88b62216fb2527b9a302","tid":1548428,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"有些人會問: 為什麼我在東, 牠會面向著西?<br />\n<br />\n其實兔子<em><ins>側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</ins></em>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)&nbsp;<em><ins>你在牠後面也會看到你</ins></em>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱。另外也有遠視。<br />\n<br />\n兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">親人的動物：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFARhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=bdbc7242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFARhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=e23087c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子的行為解釋網站：</span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFARhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=68e79f66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFARhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=65491b12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFARhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=bd1aa5ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"5fe58e5ae5b2c2a791bc8df3b8997f40f81cb162","tid":1548428,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>寵物兔是應該要被絕育</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1.&nbsp;兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2.&nbsp;絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3.&nbsp;荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4.&nbsp;兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5.&nbsp;減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"ce758d2da99c53ce64d67f34fc1f4dc5f855d0f8","tid":1548428,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"兔子發夢同主人玩：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-7b9X5x_Ro&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFARhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=b9df04bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro</a>"},{"pid":"7030e530dd1584242bb717d309625fa46a56c06d","tid":1548428,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"兔子發夢飲水:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkoTWmdwLlp8&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFARhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=a8469ae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8</a>"},{"pid":"b0b85fc890136440cb9eb69fb9158be7e0fddc78","tid":1548428,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子不滿吃飯時被拍攝，上前搞灣2部攝錄機</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lE5Qexr-jos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlE5Qexr-jos&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFARhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=386daba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lE5Qexr-jos</a>"},{"pid":"6561a200ad2f8cfed743964148c6f6fecd025537","tid":1548428,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:07:19.000Z","msg":"次次都係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地幾長壽同識唔識認人"},{"pid":"634f7204960786fa0478b2e16e3797d8468c33f1","tid":1548428,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"好臭<br />\n拎黎食好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abbbfbda8fb9c47309b140d046724bff0af1c8c","tid":1548428,"uid":91833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"634f7204960786fa0478b2e16e3797d8468c33f1","tid":1548428,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"好臭<br />\n拎黎食好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢香過你囉<br />\n你啲屎臭過佢100倍<br />\n地下有你啲屎，狗屎，兔屎你食皇種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"}]}